      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HEY BUBBA LOUIE (5) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Natisa's Secret (22.22) in a Grade 4/5. Has the early speed to give a sight. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Likely to feature again. KAELIX NITRO (4) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (23.61) in a Grade 5 at The Gardens. Solid record here winning three races. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Can do much better this time. LAKOTA COURTNEY (1) finished in the minors last start over the 300m at Taree Super Track but ran a slick 17.41 last start. Has the ability and can measure up. MY WEE LASS (2) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.",
